Hello friends,
As you probably have seen in the recent days, Joseph has gained much popularity and became a 'meme' on this page. Initially, I met Joseph on one faithful day in Senegal and we instantly became friends. A few days ago, he saw me tagging Iris in a post and saw the group on his newsfeed so he requested to join as he wanted to make new friends. However, he did not expect this to become a thing and he currently has 631 friend requests as of now (in addition to the people he has already accepted). Though he would like to be friends with you all, the constant messages and Messenger calls at midnight here from y'all have made him a bit crazy about the attention that he's been getting. Many of you have seen recent screenshots of chats that he have sent some people and were weirded out by some of his messages. Since I know Joseph personally from being with him in Senegal, I know that he only really wants to make friends and the social etiquette here is a lot different from that of the U.S. With all that, he also told me that he enjoys some of the memes that you have made and he loves UC Berkeley and would definitely want to visit the school someday, although you should probably use the money on that GoFundMe for a charity. All in all, he wishes you the best of luck on your finals and to keep memeing.
